short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Chrome extension to filter Indeed job listings.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension supports Indeed job seekers to find their desired jobs easily.
Job seekers don't want to see all jobs from all companies because some companies are consulting companies and they post same jobs here and there.
This extension will help job seekers to filter jobs by company.
